      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a feeling though. it's like the person everyone knows is just a character i'm playing to keep them happy. but there's nothing inside the suit. i'm just a hollow shell pretending to be human. what's the point of even putting in the effort to pretend anymore? it's so exhausting.",
