    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... there is no \"authentic self\" underneath. i've been playing this part for so long that even if i stopped, there's nothing there to find. it's just a void. it feels like i'm just taking up space for no reason. like i'm just a ghost haunting a life that doesn't belong to me.",
