      "content": "Feeling like there is no core self beneath the roles is a profound and difficult experience to navigate. When everything feels like a performance, the idea of a stable \"real\" self can seem unattainable. Please know that the effort you are putting into *being* is a form of existence, even if it feels like a void right now. Reaching out to a professional can help you explore these deep feelings and creativity a path toward connecting with something real again.",
